<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. ROBINSON:&nbsp; It wa=
s a one-bedroom house where we used the dining room as the living room, and=
