used to play Nerf basketball in the living
 room with the lamp shade and a Nerf basketball.&nbsp; This was before they=
 had Nerf hoops.&nbsp; (Laughter.)&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">And my mom=92s here -- re=
member we almost burned the house down because we left the ball in the lamp=
, and somebody turned the lamp on, and my mother was like, what=92s that I =
