have a hundred million channels to choose from, they=92ve
 got their iPhones and their iPads.&nbsp; So the whole range of physical ac=
tivity has changed, and as a result we=92re seeing obesity rates increase.<=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">And you can see as a pare=
