n you went back out and you played.&nbsp; And this was from
 9:30 in the morning until right before it got dark.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. WILBON:&nbsp; One of =
