 chair just out near our garage space and watch him shoot
 on the next-door neighbor=92s basket.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">And I just thought, this =
