ooked.&nbsp; They=92re scheduled.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">And that=92s where the di=
lemma comes in -- either you can=92t play outside because it=92s unsafe, or=
 you=92re the only kid playing outside because everybody else is over-speci=
alized, right?&nbsp; Because the thing about when
 we were growing up and Craig was into sports, you did every sport.&nbsp; H=
e played Little League, he played Bitty Basketball, he did the version of A=
