 because they=92ve had soda most of their live, now they have dental issues=
 that the military is covering.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">This affects all of us.&n=
bsp; Play and nutrition and overall investment in our kids -- whether they =
can read and think and engage -- it=92s just not enough for us to be okay w=
ith so many kids not having that at an excellent
 level.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">So whatever the dollar fi=
gure is, as a society, as taxpayers and as corporate America and who -- we =
should figure out how much that costs, and then pay for it.&nbsp; Period.&n=
bsp; (Applause.)&nbsp;&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">MR. WILBON:&nbsp; Yes, be=
cause we=92d pay a lot less on the front end than we=92d do on the back.&nb=
sp;
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"text-indent:.5in">Just as a way of closing,=
 it starts with all of us, those of us who, whether we=92re entrepreneurial=
 and have our own things going on, or whether we=92re working for entities =
that need to be invested locally -- and
 by locally, I mean the most local way, right there, right at home.&nbsp; W=
hen you see the neglect that has to be reversed and proactively, children w=
ho need to be introduced to this if they=92re not already.&nbsp; And obviou=
sly, Let=92s Move! and Project Play have been
 at the forefront of this for a while now, and I think we should thank Crai=
